						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Kshaya (1566 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Partly built in. Seems to record a provision made for celebrating the annual festivities for the Āḻvārs. The characters are assignable to the 16th century and the details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Kshaya, Mithuna śu. 10, Wednesday</hi> may be equated to <hi rend="bold">1566 A.D., June ·26, f.d.t. ·04.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
